    "However, contrary to our expectations, we did not find any significant differences in task performance between groups with and without reflective prompts, leading us to reject H2-2.",
    "Furthermore, the results from the perception analyses indicate that participants from all groups demonstrated a good understanding of the basic elements of a procedural text.",
    "In addressing our final research question, we studied how users revised their recipes after receiving feedback.",
    "We formulated two hypotheses to explore this aspect.",
    "Firstly, we hypothesized that the groups with reflection prompts would invest more time in the revision process."
